title: Caramelised Onion, Bacon & Mushroom Pan-Fried Cheese Toastie with Truffle Chips and Balsamic Brussels Sprouts
description: Ring in the festive season with recipes inspired by the flavours and merriment of the winter holidays. Our Caramelised Onion, Bacon & Mushroom Pan-Fried Cheese Toastie combines sweet, savoury and earthy flavours for an elevated version of family favourite cheese toasties. Serve with truffle chips and balsamic seasonal sprouts for extra cosiness.
